_sText:
I've made a lot of maps but this is the first map i've made that i've considered good enough to put online!

It can play fast or slow depending on the style of playing as there are fast routes and stealthy routes as well as sniper spots around the outside.

There is quite a lot of cover but even in 1v1 games, the game usually ends within a minute or two and in larger games the map holds out very well.

Try it and give me feedback!

NOTE: I have created a server which is running most of the time on this map,
